descriptionNullable:
"**Traffic Sign Detection Dataset**: 
This dataset comprises a collection of images, each containing various types of traffic signs commonly found on roads in Iran. 
It serves as a valuable resource for training and evaluating computer vision models aimed at detecting and recognizing traffic signs in real-world traffic scenarios. The dataset includes diverse lighting conditions, weather variations, and sign placements, making it suitable for developing robust and accurate traffic sign detection algorithms."
